  "response": "To help you effectively, I'll need more information about the specific circuit you are trying to create. Here are some details you might consider providing:\n\n1. **Components**: What components are you using? (e.g., resistors, capacitors, microcontrollers, sensors, etc.)\n\n2. **Functionality**: What do you want the circuit to accomplish? (e.g., powering a device, sensing an input, generating an output, etc.)\n\n3. **Connection Type**: Are you looking to make a breadboard connection, a soldered connection, or a PCB connection?\n\n4. **Power Source**: What power source are you using? (e.g., battery, USB, wall adapter, etc.)\n\n5. **Circuit Diagram**: If you have a diagram or schematic, that would be extremely helpful.\n\nWith this information, I can provide you with a clearer guide on how to make the connections you need in your circuit.",
